Y'know something that bothers me about this? I always love the stories where Harley breaks up with Joker, but this one...
In the theatrical cut of Suicide Squad, it seemed like this version of Joker actually seemed to care about Harley. Breaking into prison to save her is something Joker never does and seeing the two of them together was actually kind of cute (for a given value of cute).
This might be just because they cut most of Joker's screentime (to the betterment of the film) so we didn't see any abusive moments.
